# Customer Churn Prediction (Production-Level ML Project)

End-to-end Customer Churn Prediction system built using real IBM Telecom dataset.

## 🚀 Features
- Data preprocessing pipeline
- Feature encoding
- RandomForest classifier
- Model evaluation (Precision, Recall, F1, ROC-AUC)
- Model persistence using joblib
- Production-style project structure

## 📊 Dataset
IBM Telco Customer Churn Dataset (Kaggle)

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- FastAPI (planned)
- Docker (planned)

## ▶️ Run Project

```bash
python -m src.evaluate